has been enacted.&#10;3. It is important to note that the discussion centers around amendments to a Bill regarding the prohibition of physical punishment and the need for an awareness-raising campaign. Finch-Saunders AM emphasizes the importance of public awareness but does not provide concrete examples of legislation with indefinite public awareness campaigns.">
