s why the Welsh Government has deviated from this course of action in their amendment. [Interruption.] Should our amendment be agreed—&#10;Speaker: Lynne Neagle AM&#10;Content: Are you taking an intervention?&#10;Speaker: Janet Finch-Saunders AM&#10;Content: No. I'd rather crack on, to be honest.&#10;Speaker: Lynne Neagle AM&#10;Content: Okay. I can call you in the">
