ere is no direct information about specific measures the Deputy Minister is willing to take as stated in the question, she does express her commitment to a public awareness campaign and agrees to consider Amendment 2B. The discussion around Amendment 2C implies that there should be no delays in the commencement date due to this report requirement.">
